title: Price Reduced Beautiful Home on Half Acre Fruit Trees
text:
Price Reduced Beautiful Home on Half Acre Fruit Trees & ad date: 09/30/2015 
Beautiful Home on Half Acre Fruit Trees & Roses Galore 357 N. Brookings, Smith River, CA Beautiful home w/2 bath & 2 bdrm, large family room and large play room or could be bedroom. Hot tub enclosed in room near living room. Large workshop has a swimming pool and bath with cabinets. Swimming pool could be covered - is not in good condition. The backyard has about every fruit tree there is, plus a rose garden & fish pond that needs a little work. Kitchen has granite & stainless steel appliances w/wonderful cabinets & great storage. Near school. Close to OR border. MLS 1500043 $199,000 Shirley Selman, Agent 785 E. Washington Blvd #2, Crescent City Office: 707-465-2121
